text:
The product I was looking for was sold by plenty. I got the best price from Dyers RV, The FREE shipping was an absolute bonus. Shipped and received in less time than I can get from some Amazon sites. I'm three states away. Absolutely IMPRESSED will shop and buy from again. I own a 2009 Alumascape. 36', 18' awning.
Thank You Dyers RV
